TITLE: Fixing requestAnimationFrame in Testing Environment
DESCRIPTION: Implementation to fix requestAnimationFrame behavior in Vitest with jsdom by providing a custom implementation using setTimeout.
SOURCE: https://github.com/testing-library/testing-library-docs/blob/main/docs/svelte-testing-library/faq.mdx#2025-04-12_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
beforeEach(() => {
  const raf = fn => setTimeout(() => fn(new Date()), 16)
  vi.stubGlobal('requestAnimationFrame', raf)
})

// Alternatively, set `unstubGlobals: true` in vitest.config.js
afterEach(() => {
  vi.unstubAllGlobals()
})
```

